reviewText: I love the old westerns even when resolution is not like we see today or acting for that matter but that's what makes it great

LEGENDS OF THE WEST VOL 5 is ECHO BRIDGE's final 8 disc collection of public domain westerns. Stars include Roy Rogers, Tex Ritter, Gene Autry, the Three Mesquiteers, Cisco Kid, Hoot Gibson, the Range Riders and other old favorites. Transfer quality of these unrestored pictures is good to average. No bonus features or extras. Actors appearing in uncredited or supporting roles: TV's Superman George Reeves (as Jesse James!) and both of his Lois Lanes (Noel Neill & Phyllis Coates), George Montgomery, 3 Stooges comic foil Christine McIntyre, Our Gang's "Spanky," Rita Hayworth, KING KONG lead Robert Armstrong, child star Dickie Jones and Robert Walker. Also from ECHO BRIDGE: LEGENDS OF THE WEST VOL 4 contains 32 vintage western programmers. That's 31 hours of entertainment on 8 DVDs, for one low price. Parenthetical numbers preceding titles are 1 to 10 viewer poll ratings found at a film resource website.
